            "id": "4540261",
            "title": "Barrick Mining names Helen Cai as new finance chief",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li><span>Barrick Mining (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/B\" title=\"Barrick Mining Corporation\">B</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20368082-barrick-announces-finance-leadership-transition\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"named\">named</a> Helen Cai as its new CFO, effective March 1, 2026, replacing Graham Shuttleworth. This appointment is part of ongoing leadership changes at the company.</span></li>\n<li><span>Helen Cai, a board member since 2021, brings over two decades of experience in equity research, corporate finance, and M&amp;A from firms like Goldman Sachs and China International Capital.</span></li>\n<li><span>The CFO change follows CEO Mark Bristow's abrupt exit in September 2025 and other senior departures under interim CEO Mark Hill.</span></li>\n<li><span>The company is expected to report its Q4 and FY reports on February 5.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
